#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1317
msgid ""
"Please enter message for auto replying hot call when idle.\n"
"\n"
"Press [Esc] or [Cancel] or [empty content] means you will disable this "
"function\n"
"Press [OK] to keep current setting\n"
"(Not support BBMan format message)"
msgstr "請輸入閒置時自動回覆熱線呼叫的訊息。\n\n按 [Esc]、[取消] 或 [留空] 表示您將停用此功能\n按 [確定] 以保留目前設定\n（不支援 BBMan 格式化訊息）"
"請輸入閒置時要回傳什麼字串給丟水球給你的人\n"
"\n"
"按下 [Esc] 或 [Cancel] 或 [把內容清空] 將代表您想要取消這個機制\n"
"不想更改設定請直接按 [OK] 即可\n"
"( 不支援 BBMan 格式化訊息 )"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1317
msgid "Auto hot call reply"
msgstr "自動水球回覆"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1321
msgid "Disable auto hot call reply?"
msgstr "要取消自動回覆水球機制？"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1327
msgid ""
"This program has built in auto reconnect function.\n"
"Some BBS (like KKCity) is hard to connect for sometime. This program will "
"retry connecting till connected. "
msgstr "本程式內建自動重連功能。\n有些 BBS（如 KKCity）有時很難連線。本程式將會持續重試直到連線成功。"
"此程式已內建自動重新連線機制。\n"
"某些 BBS （例如 KKCity） 在某些時段常常會無法連上，這時此程式會自動重新連線，"
"直到連上為止。"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1346
msgid ""
"Please choose which shortcut message you want to edit.\n"
"\n"
"(Support BBMAN format message. Please refer [Help] How to edit BBMan format "
"message.)"
msgstr "請選擇您想要編輯哪一條快速訊息。\n\n（支援 BBMAN 格式化訊息。請參考 [說明] 如何編輯 BBMan 格式化訊息。）"
"請選擇要編輯哪個快速鍵訊息？\n"
"\n"
"( 支援 BBMan 格式化訊息。請參考選單 [說明] 編輯 BBMan 格式化訊息的方法 )"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1354
msgid ""
"Edit shortcut message.\n"
"\n"
"(Empty or choose [Cancel] means cancel this shortcut message.)"
msgstr "編輯快速訊息。\n\n（留空或選擇 [取消] 代表清除此快速訊息。）"
"編輯快速鍵訊息\n"
"\n"
"( 清空或選取 [Cancel] 代表取消此快速鍵訊息 )"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1358
msgid "Are you sure to delete this canned message?"
msgstr "確定要刪除此罐裝訊息？"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1375
msgid ""
"Please assign sound player program\n"
"\n"
"For example: esdplay / artsplay / xmms."
msgstr "請指定音效播放程式\n\n例如：esdplay / artsplay / xmms。"
"請指定用來播放聲音的程式\n"
"\n"
"例如：esdplay / artsplay / xmms"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1378
msgid "You canceled assigning sound player program."
msgstr "您取消指定播放聲音的程式"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1387
msgid "Open sound file"
msgstr "開啟聲音檔案"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1389
msgid "Open sound file. (Only accept .wav format)"
msgstr "開啟聲音檔案（僅接受 .wav 格式）"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1399
msgid ""
"You just cancel choosing. Do you want to cancel playing sound file, instead "
"of system beep when receiving hot call?"
msgstr "您取消了選擇。您是否希望在收到熱線呼叫時改用系統嗶聲，而不是播放音效檔？"
"您剛剛取消了選取。是否想要取消播放聲音檔案，在接到水球時，以系統逼聲代替？"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1409
msgid ""
"Please set max letters for pasting ( number has to be between 5 ~ 100 )\n"
"\n"
"If some lines out of max number, system sill auto wrap.\n"
"This function will auto detect Chinese and English character. Will not cut "
"in word."
msgstr "請設定貼上的最大字元數（數字必須介於 5 到 100 之間）\n\n如果某些行超出最大數量，系統將會自動換行。\n此功能會自動偵測中英文字元，不會在中文字中間切斷。"
"請設定貼上文字時每行最大長度（數字需界於 5 ~ 100 之間）\n"
"\n"
"若某行文字超出指定長度時程式會自動斷行\n"
"此機制會自動偵測中文字和英文，不會使中文和英文字被截成兩半"

#: src/frm_telnet.cpp:1410
msgid "Auto wrap when paste"
msgstr "貼上時自動斷行"

